Skills.Name: Butterfly Twirl
Skills.Description: Raises Healing Boost of single ally with lowest HP by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 10s. Recovers HP of all allies within 150 cm of ally with lowest HP by <color=red>{1}%</color> of ATK. Further raises DEF by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 15s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises Healing Boost of single ally. Recovers HP of all allies within range, raises DEF

Skills.Name: Innocent Flutter
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all Attacker allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Also raises Speed by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 13s. Also carries a 30% chance to raise ATK by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 13s. Further carries a 30% chance to raise CRIT Rate by <color=red>{3}%</color> for 13s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all Attacker allies, raises Speed, carries a chance to raise ATK and CRIT Rate

Skills.Name: Song of Flames
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> of ATK. Also raises ATK by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 10s. Also raises DEF by <color=red>{2}%</color> for 10s. Further cancels all Bleed and Poison effects.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies, raises ATK and DEF, cancels Bleed and Poison effect(s)

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Recovers HP of all allies by <color=red>5.00%-50.00%</color> according to Combo Bonus. Inflicts 100.00% DMG.
Skills.ShortDescription: Recovers HP of all allies. Inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Flower in the Rough
Skills.Description: Each time ally's HP is recovered by self, shields DMG (<color=red>{0}%</color> of skill user's ATK) of all allies for 15s. (CT 1s)
Skills.ShortDescription: Each time ally's HP is recovered by self, shields DMG of all allies
